{{ 'ka-faq-main.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
{%- comment -%}
  Resync marker 2026-07-22: this file and templates/page.faq.json did
  not sync to the staging theme on the first push (confirmed via a
  direct Admin API files() query -- both came back with zero nodes
  while every other file from the same commit landed correctly, the
  same failure pattern documented in CLAUDE.md's 2026-07-11 incident
  note). This trivial edit forces a fresh commit touching this file so
  the GitHub->Shopify connector has something new to sync.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%}
  K&A FAQ — Intro + Search + Topic Nav + Q&A List
  Spec: Docs/faq-build-spec.md, Section 3 (S2 "Intro + Search", S3 "Topic
  Nav", S4 "FAQ List"). Prototype: Prototypes/faq-v1.html.

  Combined into one section (not three) because the interaction logic is
  genuinely shared/coupled: the topic chips clear the search field, the
  search filter hides/shows accordion rows AND collapses empty category
  groups, and the scroll-tracked active chip observes the same .faq-group
  elements the search filter toggles. Splitting this into separate
  sections would mean coordinating one JS file across independently
  re-orderable sections for no real editorial benefit (Suraj cannot
  usefully reorder "search" relative to "topic nav" — their order is
  fixed by the page's own logic). Each Q&A pair IS its own block, so
  content stays fully editable per CLAUDE.md's requirement.

  NAV STATE — no page-scoped override needed. FAQ has no hero image (see
  spec §2, "Why no hero"), and the settled/crystallised nav state is
  already applied unconditionally to every non-home template via the
  is_home check in sections/ka-nav.liquid — confirmed by reading that
  file directly, not assumed from the prototype. Every non-index template
  (Collection, Product, Cart, Page, Blog, Article, Search, 404 — and now
  FAQ) already renders nav permanently settled from first paint. The
  Collection page's own #ka-nav override (referenced by the spec/
  prototype as the technique to reproduce) is therefore a harmless no-op
  layered on top of that same centralised mechanism, not a second
  independent one — nothing further is required here.

  STICKY OFFSET (spec §4/§7 flag F4) — the spec flags `top: 104px` for
  the sticky topic bar as reasoned from precedent, asking this to be
  confirmed against the live nav CSS rather than trusted blindly.
  Confirmed: assets/ka-product-main.css `.ka-media` and assets/
  ka-cart-summary.css `.ka-summary` both already use `top: 104px` for a
  sticky element on this exact page family (hero-less, permanently-
  settled nav) — this is a real, already-shipped, verified value, not
  just the prototype's guess. Independently recomputed from ka-nav.css's
  real box model (utility bar + settled nav padding/content/border) and
  confirmed 104px is correct at desktop. See ka-faq-main.css for the
  one deliberate deviation from the prototype found during this check
  (the mobile `top: 0` value, which the same recomputation shows would
  overlap the fixed header — not reproduced here).
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="faq-intro">
  <p class="eyebrow faq-intro__eyebrow reveal">{{ section.settings.intro_eyebrow }}</p>
  <h1 class="faq-intro__title reveal reveal-delay-1">
    <span class="lead">{{ section.settings.intro_title_lead }}</span>
    <span class="main">{{ section.settings.intro_title_main }}</span>
  </h1>
  <p class="faq-intro__body reveal reveal-delay-2">{{ section.settings.intro_body }}</p>

  <div class="faq-search reveal reveal-delay-3">
    <div class="faq-search__field">
      <span class="faq-search__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="10.5" cy="10.5" r="6.5"/><path d="M20 20l-4.8-4.8"/></svg>
      </span>
      <input
        type="text"
        class="faq-search__input"
        id="faqSearch"
        placeholder="{{ section.settings.search_placeholder }}"
        aria-label="Search frequently asked questions"
      />
      <button type="button" class="faq-search__clear" id="faqSearchClear">{{ section.settings.search_clear_label | default: 'Clear' }}</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="faq-topics" id="faqTopics">
  <span class="faq-topics__label">{{ section.settings.topics_label | default: 'Topics' }}</span>
  <div class="faq-topics__chips" id="topicChips">
    <button class="ka-chip" type="button" data-target="cat-corset">{{ section.settings.cat_corset_title }}</button>
    <button class="ka-chip" type="button" data-target="cat-sizing">{{ section.settings.cat_sizing_title }}</button>
    <button class="ka-chip" type="button" data-target="cat-ordering">{{ section.settings.cat_ordering_title }}</button>
    <button class="ka-chip" type="button" data-target="cat-shipping">{{ section.settings.cat_shipping_title }}</button>
  </div>
</div>

{%- liquid
  assign first_open = false
-%}

<div class="faq-list" id="faqList">

  <!-- Group 1 — The Corset, Explained -->
  <section class="faq-group" id="cat-corset" data-cat="corset">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--muted faq-group__num">{{ section.settings.cat_corset_num }}</p>
    <h2 class="faq-group__title">{{ section.settings.cat_corset_title }}</h2>
    <p class="faq-group__dek">{{ section.settings.cat_corset_dek }}</p>
    <div class="ka-accordion">
      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        {%- if block.settings.category == 'corset' -%}
          {%- assign is_first = false -%}
          {%- unless first_open -%}{%- assign is_first = true -%}{%- assign first_open = true -%}{%- endunless -%}
          {%- render 'ka-faq-acc', block: block, is_first: is_first -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Group 2 — Sizing & Occasion -->
  <section class="faq-group" id="cat-sizing" data-cat="sizing">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--muted faq-group__num">{{ section.settings.cat_sizing_num }}</p>
    <h2 class="faq-group__title">{{ section.settings.cat_sizing_title }}</h2>
    <p class="faq-group__dek">{{ section.settings.cat_sizing_dek }}</p>
    <div class="ka-accordion">
      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        {%- if block.settings.category == 'sizing' -%}
          {%- assign is_first = false -%}
          {%- unless first_open -%}{%- assign is_first = true -%}{%- assign first_open = true -%}{%- endunless -%}
          {%- render 'ka-faq-acc', block: block, is_first: is_first -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Group 3 — Ordering & Policy -->
  <section class="faq-group" id="cat-ordering" data-cat="ordering">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--muted faq-group__num">{{ section.settings.cat_ordering_num }}</p>
    <h2 class="faq-group__title">{{ section.settings.cat_ordering_title }}</h2>
    <p class="faq-group__dek">{{ section.settings.cat_ordering_dek }}</p>
    <div class="ka-accordion">
      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        {%- if block.settings.category == 'ordering' -%}
          {%- assign is_first = false -%}
          {%- unless first_open -%}{%- assign is_first = true -%}{%- assign first_open = true -%}{%- endunless -%}
          {%- render 'ka-faq-acc', block: block, is_first: is_first -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Group 4 — Shipping & Care -->
  <section class="faq-group" id="cat-shipping" data-cat="shipping">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--muted faq-group__num">{{ section.settings.cat_shipping_num }}</p>
    <h2 class="faq-group__title">{{ section.settings.cat_shipping_title }}</h2>
    <p class="faq-group__dek">{{ section.settings.cat_shipping_dek }}</p>
    <div class="ka-accordion">
      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        {%- if block.settings.category == 'shipping' -%}
          {%- assign is_first = false -%}
          {%- unless first_open -%}{%- assign is_first = true -%}{%- assign first_open = true -%}{%- endunless -%}
          {%- render 'ka-faq-acc', block: block, is_first: is_first -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- No-search-results state — verbatim adaptation of .ka-collection-empty
       (assets/ka-collection-grid.css), reused for zero search matches. -->
  <div class="ka-faq-empty" id="faqEmpty">
    <h3 class="ka-faq-empty__title">{{ section.settings.empty_title }}</h3>
    <p class="ka-faq-empty__body">{{ section.settings.empty_body }}</p>
    <a href="https://wa.me/{{ settings.whatsapp_number }}" class="btn-outline-rose" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ section.settings.empty_cta_label }}</a>
  </div>

</div>

<script src="{{ 'ka-faq.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ — Intro, Topics & List",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "ka-faq-main-section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Intro & search"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "intro_eyebrow", "label": "Eyebrow", "default": "Frequently Asked Questions" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "intro_title_lead", "label": "Title — small lead-in line", "default": "Every Question," },
    { "type": "text", "id": "intro_title_main", "label": "Title — large main word", "default": "Answered Quietly" },
    { "type": "textarea", "id": "intro_body", "label": "Intro body copy", "default": "Every Karishma & Ashita piece is made to order, by hand — which naturally invites questions before you begin. We've gathered the ones we're asked most often here, so you can find what you need before a single message is sent. For anything more particular to you, our styling concierge is always a conversation away." },
    { "type": "text", "id": "search_placeholder", "label": "Search field placeholder", "default": "Search a question — sizing, pricing, shipping…" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "search_clear_label", "label": "Search \"Clear\" label", "default": "Clear" },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Topic nav"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "topics_label", "label": "Topics bar label", "default": "Topics" },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Category 1 — The Corset, Explained"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cat_corset_num", "label": "Numbered eyebrow", "default": "01 — Understanding K&A" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cat_corset_title", "label": "Category title", "default": "The Corset, Explained" },
    { "type": "textarea", "id": "cat_corset_dek", "label": "Supporting line", "default": "What a K&A corset actually is, and how construction — not just cut — is what sets it apart." },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Category 2 — Sizing & Occasion"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cat_sizing_num", "label": "Numbered eyebrow", "default": "02 — Fit & Occasion" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cat_sizing_title", "label": "Category title", "default": "Sizing & Occasion" },
    { "type": "textarea", "id": "cat_sizing_dek", "label": "Supporting line", "default": "Getting the fit right, and finding the piece for your moment — bridal or otherwise." },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Category 3 — Ordering & Policy"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cat_ordering_num", "label": "Numbered eyebrow", "default": "03 — Ordering" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cat_ordering_title", "label": "Category title", "default": "Ordering & Policy" },
    { "type": "textarea", "id": "cat_ordering_dek", "label": "Supporting line", "default": "What a piece costs, how long it takes, and what's possible to change along the way." },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Category 4 — Shipping & Care"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cat_shipping_num", "label": "Numbered eyebrow", "default": "04 — After Ordering" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cat_shipping_title", "label": "Category title", "default": "Shipping & Care" },
    { "type": "textarea", "id": "cat_shipping_dek", "label": "Supporting line", "default": "From our studio to your door, and how to keep a piece beautiful for years after." },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "No-search-results state"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "empty_title", "label": "Title", "default": "We couldn't find a match for that." },
    { "type": "textarea", "id": "empty_body", "label": "Body", "default": "Our styling concierge would love to help directly — send us your question and we'll answer personally, usually within the day." },
    { "type": "text", "id": "empty_cta_label", "label": "CTA label", "default": "Ask Our Styling Concierge" }
  ],
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "question",
      "name": "Question (plain answer)",
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "select",
          "id": "category",
          "label": "Category",
          "options": [
            { "value": "corset", "label": "The Corset, Explained" },
            { "value": "sizing", "label": "Sizing & Occasion" },
            { "value": "ordering", "label": "Ordering & Policy" },
            { "value": "shipping", "label": "Shipping & Care" }
          ],
          "default": "corset"
        },
        { "type": "text", "id": "question", "label": "Question" },
        { "type": "richtext", "id": "answer", "label": "Answer", "info": "Use the link tool for any inline links (e.g. to a Journal article or /pages/contact)." }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "question_timeline",
      "name": "Question (with lead-time list)",
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "Same as \"Question\", but renders a bulleted lead-time list (the em-dash bullet style already used by the product-page accordion) between an intro and an outro paragraph. Built for the made-to-order timelines answer specifically."
        },
        {
          "type": "select",
          "id": "category",
          "label": "Category",
          "options": [
            { "value": "corset", "label": "The Corset, Explained" },
            { "value": "sizing", "label": "Sizing & Occasion" },
            { "value": "ordering", "label": "Ordering & Policy" },
            { "value": "shipping", "label": "Shipping & Care" }
          ],
          "default": "ordering"
        },
        { "type": "text", "id": "question", "label": "Question" },
        { "type": "richtext", "id": "intro", "label": "Intro paragraph (before the list)" },
        { "type": "text", "id": "lead_drapes", "label": "Lead time — Drapes / corset drape sarees" },
        { "type": "text", "id": "lead_indowestern", "label": "Lead time — Indo-Western sets" },
        { "type": "text", "id": "lead_lehengas", "label": "Lead time — Lehengas" },
        { "type": "richtext", "id": "outro", "label": "Outro paragraph (after the list)" }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "FAQ — Intro, Topics & List" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
